snippet.title: Mario Strikers: Battle League - So Much Fun It Hurts - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
You're gonna get hit with the unexpected in Mario Strikers: Battle League! Tackle, pass, and score your way to victory in this chaotic soccer-ish sport. It'll be so much fun, it hurts! Available June 10th only on Nintendo Switch. ESRB Rating: Everyone 10 and Up with Cartoon Violence, Comic Mischief

Pre-order today: http://ninten.do/6008bK13g
